{"id": 1168, "genre": 1001, "title": "现如今你进行日常运动有什么困扰？", "description": "离开了学校，你的运动热情如何安放？", "record_count": 2159, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160813095515kwDd7l54p6K91MEU.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-08-17T03:15:41Z", "options": [{"id": 108182, "content": "懒", "image": null, "praise_count": 405, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 296767}, {"id": 107171, "content": "找不到人少便宜离家近的运动场地", "image": null, "praise_count": 499, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 107172, "content": "没有专业人士指导，运动技能点越来越低", "image": null, "praise_count": 55, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 108181, "content": "占用其他日常时间", "image": null, "praise_count": 46, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 216033}, {"id": 108183, "content": "喜欢在操场跑步 可惜所有学校的操场都不对外", "image": null, "praise_count": 162, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 479437}, {"id": 108185, "content": "加班", "image": null, "praise_count": 123, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 667615}, {"id": 108186, "content": "还好没毕业??", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 696679}, {"id": 107169, "content": "篮球足球无法凑齐队友", "image": null, "praise_count": 52, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 107170, "content": "和陌生人组队我的出色传球技能都得不到发挥", "image": null, "praise_count": 57, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 107174, "content": "说要解决约伴、找地的app挺多，但不知道该选哪个", "image": null, "praise_count": 39, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 107175, "content": "报了网球羽毛球班，总懒得去", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 108289, "content": "左三圈右三圈，脖子扭扭，屁股扭扭。平时没事，踢踢腿也是好的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 707545}, {"id": 108290, "content": "只是想一想。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 719332}, {"id": 108291, "content": "想找个足球场 踢场球，发现要么收费 要么场烂 要么人多", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 713384}, {"id": 108293, "content": "打球的伙伴固定，自己球技遇到瓶颈，热情越来越低", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 645237}, {"id": 108294, "content": "找不到志同道合 时间吻合的人，场地太远?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 710190}, {"id": 108806, "content": "懒", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 722973}, {"id": 108295, "content": "关键还是懒", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 719557}, {"id": 108296, "content": "一会儿下班就要去健身房了，别拦我", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 691495}, {"id": 108552, "content": "隔天健身，每次出门拎着运动鞋运动衣一大包，很忧愁，带着这么一大坨怎么fashion得起来啊生气！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 460062}, {"id": 108297, "content": "踢足球凑不齐啊，也找不着室内的", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1248414}, {"id": 108298, "content": "北京习惯了每周打3次网球，定居南京后完全约不到球友了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 719564}, {"id": 108299, "content": "天天跟老婆啪啪啪哪有力气去跑步", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 268023}, {"id": 108300, "content": "手指运动太多", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 511481}, {"id": 108301, "content": "没人一起?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 676287}, {"id": 108302, "content": "下了决心运动时下雨，性质没了大晴天", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 717276}, {"id": 108815, "content": "所有的运动视频，技巧等等全是收藏不看系列?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 723023}, {"id": 108560, "content": "老胳膊老腿怕伤残", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 721068}, {"id": 108308, "content": "要加班！没时间！", "image": "img/option/option/20160817172831KXxlFHizT325BkVc.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 719610}, {"id": 108309, "content": "没有 【日】常运动  的对象", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 261234}, {"id": 111125, "content": "羽毛球好贵的说…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 734105}, {"id": 108310, "content": "找不到可以一起坚持的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 710750}, {"id": 108311, "content": "已经习惯了一个人漫无目的的压马路！", "image": "img/option/option/20160817174831x5aBXcrbOmp2ltMH", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 719636}, {"id": 108314, "content": "额，为什么呢", "image": "img/option/option/20160817175955StcXvEdhIMW9DAYN.jpg", "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 613182}, {"id": 108315, "content": "没有了陪伴的小伙伴", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 395998}, {"id": 108316, "content": "额 这是为什么呢", "image": "img/option/option/20160817180150iCjKJZeIENtkUxlr.jpg", "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 613182}, {"id": 108318, "content": "Heh", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 702632}, {"id": 108319, "content": "学习压力太大，忙起来就没时间了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 461}, {"id": 108320, "content": "害怕被空气毒死", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 562166}, {"id": 108321, "content": "找不到水平相当的对手....很忧伤", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 378869}, {"id": 108322, "content": "想打篮球，找不到同好的女生", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 719672}, {"id": 108323, "content": "很想晨练想呼吸新鲜空气然而又怕晒?", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 698323}, {"id": 109603, "content": "内心非常想动，就是没人逼我", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 726047}, {"id": 108324, "content": "天气太热", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 653450}, {"id": 108325, "content": 